  <summary date="2019-08-21T15:37:23Z" status="Introduced in House">Allied Health Workforce Diversity Act of 2019This bill allows the Department of Health and Human Services to provide grants to accredited education programs to increase diversity in the physical-therapy, occupational-therapy, audiology, and speech-language pathology professions. Grants may be used to provide scholarships or to support recruitment and retention of students from underrepresented groups.</summary>
